## Proposed Changes

### Phase 1: Repository Foundation (Day 1)

#### [NEW] Root `package.json` вЂ” pnpm workspace root
#### [NEW] `pnpm-workspace.yaml` вЂ” defines packages/* and apps/* as workspaces
#### [NEW] `turbo.json` вЂ” Turborepo pipeline for build/test/lint caching
#### [NEW] `tsconfig.base.json` вЂ” shared TypeScript config
#### [NEW] `.eslintrc.js` вЂ” shared ESLint config

---

### Phase 2: Design Tokens Package (Day 1)

#### [NEW] `packages/tokens/src/tokens.css`
All tokens exposed as CSS custom properties:
- `--color-primary-*`, `--color-secondary-*`, `--color-success-*`, `--color-warning-*`, `--color-error-*`, `--color-neutral-*`
- `--font-family-*`, `--font-size-*`, `--font-weight-*`, `--line-height-*`
- `--spacing-xs/sm/md/lg/xl`
- `--radius-sm/md/lg/full`
- `--shadow-sm/md/lg`
- Dark mode variant via `[data-theme="dark"]` selector

#### [NEW] `packages/tokens/src/tokens.ts` вЂ” typed JS token object mirroring CSS vars

---

### Phase 3: UI Component Library (Day 2вЂ“3)

#### [NEW] `packages/ui/vite.config.ts` вЂ” library mode, dual CJS+ESM output
#### [NEW] `packages/ui/src/components/Button/` вЂ” full Button component
  - Variants: `primary | secondary | ghost | danger`
  - Sizes: `sm | md | lg`
  - States: loading spinner, disabled, icon support
  - ARIA: `role="button"`, keyboard nav

#### [NEW] `packages/ui/src/components/Input/` вЂ” Input component
